{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01FefS4wb43kAV4T7XidPFMC","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.api;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbProperty;\n     4→import jakarta.validation.constraints.*;\n     5→import lombok.*;\n     6→\n     7→import jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.*;\n     8→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.api.PetListDto;\n     9→\n    10→import java.io.Serializable;\n    11→import java.util.*;\n    12→\n    13→/**\n    14→ * Created with IntelliJ IDEA.\n    15→ * User: tw\n    16→ * Date: 01.01.14\n    17→ * Time: 21:08\n    18→ * To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.\n    19→ */\n    20→@Getter\n    21→@Setter\n    22→@ToString\n    23→@EqualsAndHashCode(callSuper = false)\n    24→@NoArgsConstructor\n    25→@AllArgsConstructor\n    26→@XmlRootElement(name = \"owner\")\n    27→public class OwnerDto implements Serializable {\n    28→\n    29→    private static final long serialVersionUID = 7995827646591579744L;\n    30→\n    31→    @NotNull\n    32→    @JsonbProperty\n    33→    private Long id;\n    34→\n    35→    @NotBlank\n    36→    @JsonbProperty\n    37→    private UUID uuid;\n    38→\n    39→    @NotEmpty\n    40→    @JsonbProperty\n    41→    private String firstName;\n    42→\n    43→    @NotEmpty\n    44→    @JsonbProperty\n    45→    private String lastName;\n    46→\n    47→    @NotEmpty\n    48→    @JsonbProperty\n    49→    private String address;\n    50→\n    51→    @NotEmpty\n    52→    @JsonbProperty\n    53→    private String houseNumber;\n    54→\n    55→    @NotEmpty\n    56→    @JsonbProperty\n    57→    private String addressInfo;\n    58→\n    59→    @NotEmpty\n    60→    @JsonbProperty\n    61→    private String city;\n    62→\n    63→    @NotEmpty\n    64→    @JsonbProperty\n    65→    @Digits(fraction = 0, integer = 5)\n    66→    private String zipCode;\n    67→\n    68→    @NotEmpty\n    69→    @JsonbProperty\n    70→    @Pattern(regexp = \"\\\\+[1-9][0-9]{9,14}\", message = \"{invalid.phoneNumber}\")\n    71→    private String phoneNumber;\n    72→\n    73→    @JsonbProperty\n    74→    private PetListDto petList = new PetListDto();\n    75→\n    76→}\n    77→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VJkzMqx2rHx6eG7ZLsPXTM","session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"43248dec-4067-450b-a426-ebe51dd0e677"}
