{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LWbCgCUqmgBGCgmBGrp7GL","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n     2→\n     3→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\n     4→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n     5→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n     6→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n     7→\n     8→import java.io.Serializable;\n     9→import java.util.List;\n    10→\n    11→public interface OwnerViewService extends Serializable {\n    12→\n    13→    List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner);\n    14→\n    15→    String getPetsAsString(Owner owner);\n    16→\n    17→    List<Visit> getVisits(Pet ownersPet);\n    18→\n    19→    Visit addNewVisit(Visit visit);\n    20→\n    21→    Pet addNewPet(Pet pet);\n    22→\n    23→    Pet findPetById(long id);\n    24→\n    25→    Pet updatePet(Pet pet);\n    26→\n    27→    Owner findOwnerById(long id);\n    28→\n    29→    Owner updateOwner(Owner entity);\n    30→\n    31→    Owner addNewOwner(Owner entity);\n    32→\n    33→    void deleteOwner(long ownerId);\n    34→\n    35→    List<Owner> getAllOwner();\n    36→\n    37→    List<Owner> searchOwner(String searchterm);\n    38→\n    39→    PetType findPetTypeById(long petTypeId);\n    40→\n    41→    List<PetType> getAllPetType();\n    42→\n    43→}\n    44→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VJkzMqx2rHx6eG7ZLsPXTM","session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"8a90066e-0e63-4d9f-9e08-8b373d528bec"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012d4Djg6f5PYP4iJaJWwL7i","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\n     4→import jakarta.annotation.PreDestroy;\n     5→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n     6→import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;\n     7→import lombok.extern.java.Log;\n     8→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\n     9→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n    10→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db.PetDao;\n    11→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n    12→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db.PetTypeDao;\n    13→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db.PetTypeService;\n    14→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n    15→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db.VisitDao;\n    16→\n    17→import java.io.Serializable;\n    18→import java.util.List;\n    19→\n    20→@Log\n    21→@Stateless\n    22→public class OwnerViewServiceImpl implements OwnerViewService, Serializable {\n    23→\n    24→    private static final long serialVersionUID = -553095668269912269L;\n    25→\n    26→    @EJB\n    27→    private PetTypeDao petTypeDao;\n    28→\n    29→    @EJB\n    30→    private OwnerDao ownerDao;\n    31→\n    32→    @EJB\n    33→    private VisitDao visitDao;\n    34→\n    35→    @EJB\n    36→    private PetDao petDao;\n    37→\n    38→    @Override\n    39→    public void deleteOwner(long ownerId) {\n    40→        Owner owner = ownerDao.findById(ownerId);\n    41→        for(Pet pet:petDao.getPetsAsList(owner)){\n    42→            for(Visit visit:visitDao.getVisits(pet)){\n    43→                visitDao.delete(visit.getId());\n    44→            }\n    45→            petDao.delete(pet.getId());\n    46→        }\n    47→        ownerDao.delete(ownerId);\n    48→    }\n    49→\n    50→    @Override\n    51→    public List<Owner> getAllOwner() {\n    52→        return ownerDao.getAll();\n    53→    }\n    54→\n    55→    @Override\n    56→    public Owner findOwnerById(long id) {\n    57→        return ownerDao.findById(id);\n    58→    }\n    59→\n    60→    @Override\n    61→    public Owner updateOwner(Owner entity) {\n    62→        return ownerDao.update(entity);\n    63→    }\n    64→\n    65→    @Override\n    66→    public Owner addNewOwner(Owner entity) {\n    67→        return ownerDao.addNew(entity);\n    68→    }\n    69→\n    70→    @Override\n    71→    public List<Owner> searchOwner(String searchterm) {\n    72→        return ownerDao.search(searchterm);\n    73→    }\n    74→\n    75→    @Override\n    76→    public PetType findPetTypeById(long petTypeId) {\n    77→        return petTypeDao.findById(petTypeId);\n    78→    }\n    79→\n    80→    @Override\n    81→    public List<PetType> getAllPetType() {\n    82→        return petTypeDao.getAll();\n    83→    }\n    84→\n    85→    @Override\n    86→    public List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner) {\n    87→        return petDao.getPetsAsList(owner);\n    88→    }\n    89→\n    90→    @Override\n    91→    public String getPetsAsString(Owner owner) {\n    92→        StringBuilder s = new StringBuilder();\n    93→        for (Pet pet : this.getPetsAsList(owner)) {\n    94→            s.append(pet.getName())\n    95→                    .append(\" (\")\n    96→                    .append(pet.getType().getName())\n    97→                    .append(\") \");\n    98→        }\n    99→        return s.toString();\n   100→    }\n   101→\n   102→    @Override\n   103→    public Pet addNewPet(Pet pet) {\n   104→        return petDao.addNew(pet);\n   105→    }\n   106→\n   107→    @Override\n   108→    public Pet findPetById(long id) {\n   109→        return petDao.findById(id);\n   110→    }\n   111→\n   112→    @Override\n   113→    public Pet updatePet(Pet pet) {\n   114→        return petDao.update(pet);\n   115→    }\n   116→\n   117→    @Override\n   118→    public List<Visit> getVisits(Pet ownersPet) {\n   119→        return visitDao.getVisits(ownersPet);\n   120→    }\n   121→\n   122→    @Override\n   123→    public Visit addNewVisit(Visit visit) {\n   124→        return visitDao.addNew(visit);\n   125→    }\n   126→\n   127→\n   128→    @PostConstruct\n   129→    public void postConstruct() {\n   130→        log.info(\"postConstruct: \"+OwnerViewServiceImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n   131→    }\n   132→\n   133→    @PreDestroy\n   134→    public void preDestroy() {\n   135→        log.info(\"preDestroy: \"+OwnerViewServiceImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n   136→    }\n   137→}\n   138→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VJkzMqx2rHx6eG7ZLsPXTM","session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"ac3b7099-8664-4070-b51f-f8fc6d8db49a"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0135pDBxgkuvefm2pUDiPEHb","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.validation.constraints.NotNull;\n     4→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.framework.views.CrudView;\n     5→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.views.Owner2Model;\n     6→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.views.OwnersPet2Model;\n     7→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n     8→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.views.OwnersPetView;\n     9→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n    10→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.views.OwnersPetVisitView;\n    11→\n    12→import java.util.List;\n    13→\n    14→\n    15→/**\n    16→ *\n    17→ */\n    18→public interface OwnerView extends CrudView<Owner>,\n    19→        OwnersPetView,\n    20→        OwnersPetVisitView,\n    21→        Owner2Model,\n    22→        OwnersPet2Model {\n    23→\n    24→\n    25→    String JSF_PAGE = \"owner.jsf\";\n    26→\n    27→    String showOwnerEditForm();\n    28→\n    29→    List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner);\n    30→\n    31→    String getPetsAsString(Owner owner);\n    32→\n    33→    List<Visit> getVisits(Pet ownersPet);\n    34→\n    35→    long serialVersionUID = 3691413509555926089L;\n    36→}\n    37→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VJkzMqx2rHx6eG7ZLsPXTM","session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"db572f56-fc02-40dd-ac75-bf8d7046abfd"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_013DLEy3b2UGH4LPtJxoW4qH","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.ejb.EJB;\n     4→import jakarta.ejb.EJBException;\n     5→import jakarta.ejb.EJBTransactionRolledbackException;\n     6→import lombok.Getter;\n     7→import lombok.Setter;\n     8→import lombok.extern.java.Log;\n     9→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.conf.PetclinicApplication;\n    10→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.views.FlashMessagesView;\n    11→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.application.views.LanguageView;\n    12→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db.OwnerViewService;\n    13→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.views.OwnerFlowView;\n    14→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n    15→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n    16→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n    17→\n    18→import jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\n    19→import jakarta.annotation.PreDestroy;\n    20→import jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped;\n    21→import jakarta.inject.Inject;\n    22→import jakarta.inject.Named;\n    23→\n    24→import java.io.Serializable;\n    25→import java.util.List;\n    26→import java.util.UUID;\n    27→\n    28→/**\n    29→ * Created with IntelliJ IDEA.\n    30→ * User: tw\n    31→ * Date: 06.01.14\n    32→ * Time: 16:24\n    33→ * To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.\n    34→ */\n    35→@Log\n    36→@Getter\n    37→@Setter\n    38→@Named(\"ownerView\")\n    39→@SessionScoped\n    40→public class OwnerViewImpl implements OwnerView, Serializable {\n    41→\n    42→    private static final long serialVersionUID = -4809817472969005481L;\n    43→\n    44→    @Inject\n    45→    private PetclinicApplication petclinicApplication;\n    46→\n    47→    @Inject\n    48→    private LanguageView languageView;\n    49→\n    50→    @Inject\n    51→    private FlashMessagesView flashMessagesView;\n    52→\n    53→    @Inject\n    54→    private OwnerFlowView ownerFlowView;\n    55→\n    56→    /*\n    57→    @EJB\n    58→    private OwnerService entityService;\n    59→\n    60→    @EJB\n    61→    private PetService petService;\n    62→\n    63→    @EJB\n    64→    private PetTypeService petTypeService;\n    65→\n    66→    @EJB\n    67→    private VisitService visitService;\n    68→    */\n    69→\n    70→    @EJB\n    71→    private OwnerViewService ownerViewService;\n    72→\n    73→    private String searchterm;\n    74→    private List<Owner> list;\n    75→    private Owner entity;\n    76→    private Pet pet;\n    77→    private List<PetType> petTypeList;\n    78→    private long petTypeId;\n    79→    private Visit visit;\n    80→\n    81→    @Override\n    82→    public String showDetailsForm(Owner o) {\n    83→        log.info(\"showDetailsForm\");\n    84→        if (o != null) {\n    85→            this.entity = this.ownerViewService.findOwnerById(o.getId());\n    86→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n    87→        } else {\n    88→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n    89→        }\n    90→        return JSF_PAGE;\n    91→    }\n    92→\n    93→    @Override\n    94→    public  String cancelDetails(){\n    95→        log.info(\"cancelDetails\");\n    96→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n    97→        return JSF_PAGE;\n    98→    }\n    99→\n   100→    @Override\n   101→    public String showNewForm() {\n   102→        log.info(\"showNewForm\");\n   103→        this.newEntity();\n   104→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateNew();\n   105→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   106→    }\n   107→\n   108→    @Override\n   109→    public String cancelNew() {\n   110→        log.info(\"cancelNew\");\n   111→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   112→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   113→    }\n   114→\n   115→    @Override\n   116→    public String saveNew() {\n   117→        log.info(\"saveNew\");\n   118→        this.saveNewEntity();\n   119→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   120→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   121→    }\n   122→\n   123→    @Override\n   124→    public String showEditForm() {\n   125→        log.info(\"showEditForm\");\n   126→        if (this.entity != null) {\n   127→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateEdit();\n   128→        } else {\n   129→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   130→        }\n   131→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   132→    }\n   133→\n   134→    @Deprecated\n   135→    @Override\n   136→    public String showOwnerEditForm() {\n   137→        log.info(\"showOwnerEditForm\");\n   138→        if (this.entity != null) {\n   139→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateEdit();\n   140→        } else {\n   141→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   142→        }\n   143→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   144→    }\n   145→\n   146→    @Override\n   147→    public List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner) {\n   148→        return ownerViewService.getPetsAsList(owner);\n   149→    }\n   150→\n   151→    @Override\n   152→    public String getPetsAsString(Owner owner) {\n   153→        return ownerViewService.getPetsAsString(owner);\n   154→    }\n   155→\n   156→    @Override\n   157→    public List<Visit> getVisits(Pet ownersPet){\n   158→        return ownerViewService.getVisits(ownersPet);\n   159→    }\n   160→\n   161→    @Override\n   162→    public String cancelEdited() {\n   163→        log.info(\"cancelEdited\");\n   164→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   165→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   166→    }\n   167→\n   168→    @Override\n   169→    public String saveEdited() {\n   170→        log.info(\"saveEdited\");\n   171→        this.saveEditedEntity();\n   172→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   173→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   174→    }\n   175→\n   176→    @Override\n   177→    public String showDeleteForm() {\n   178→        log.info(\"showDeleteForm\");\n   179→        if (this.entity != null) {\n   180→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDelete();\n   181→        } else {\n   182→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   183→        }\n   184→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   185→    }\n   186→\n   187→    @Override\n   188→    public String cancelDelete() {\n   189→        log.info(\"cancelDelete\");\n   190→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   191→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   192→    }\n   193→\n   194→    @Override\n   195→    public String performDelete() {\n   196→        log.info(\"performDelete\");\n   197→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDelete();\n   198→        try {\n   199→            long id = this.entity.getId();\n   200→            String uuid = this.entity.getUuid().toString();\n   201→            String selectedPrimaryKey = this.entity.getPrimaryKey() + \"(\" + id + \",\" + uuid + \")\";\n   202→            this.ownerViewService.deleteOwner(this.entity.getId());\n   203→            this.entity = null;\n   204→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   205→            String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.delete.done\";\n   206→            String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   207→            flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, selectedPrimaryKey);\n   208→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   209→        } catch (EJBException e) {\n   210→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(e, this.entity);\n   211→        }\n   212→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   213→    }\n   214→\n   215→    @Override\n   216→    public String cancelOwnerPetVisitNew() {\n   217→        log.info(\"cancelOwnerPetVisitNew\");\n   218→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   219→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   220→    }\n   221→\n   222→    @Override\n   223→    public String showOwnerPetNewForm() {\n   224→        log.info(\"showOwnerPetNewForm\");\n   225→        this.pet = new Pet();\n   226→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateNewPet();\n   227→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   228→    }\n   229→\n   230→    @Override\n   231→    public String saveOwnerPetNew() {\n   232→        log.info(\"saveOwnerPetNew\");\n   233→        try {\n   234→            PetType petType = this.ownerViewService.findPetTypeById(this.petTypeId);\n   235→            this.pet.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n   236→            this.pet.setType(petType);\n   237→            this.pet.setOwner(this.entity);\n   238→            this.pet = this.ownerViewService.addNewPet(this.pet);\n   239→            String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.addNew.done\";\n   240→            String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   241→            flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, this.pet);\n   242→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   243→        } catch (EJBException e) {\n   244→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateNewPet();\n   245→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(e, this.pet);\n   246→        }\n   247→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   248→    }\n   249→\n   250→    @Override\n   251→    public String cancelOwnerPetNew() {\n   252→        log.info(\"cancelOwnerPetNew\");\n   253→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   254→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   255→    }\n   256→\n   257→    @Override\n   258→    public String showOwnerPetEditForm(Pet pet) {\n   259→        log.info(\"showOwnerPetEditForm\");\n   260→        if (pet != null) {\n   261→            this.pet = this.ownerViewService.findPetById(pet.getId());\n   262→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateEditPet();\n   263→        } else {\n   264→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   265→        }\n   266→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   267→    }\n   268→\n   269→    @Override\n   270→    public String saveOwnerPetEdit() {\n   271→        log.info(\"saveOwnerPetEdit\");\n   272→        try {\n   273→            PetType petType = this.ownerViewService.findPetTypeById(this.petTypeId);\n   274→            this.pet.setType(petType);\n   275→            this.ownerViewService.updatePet(this.pet);\n   276→            long ownerId = this.entity.getId();\n   277→            this.entity = this.ownerViewService.findOwnerById(ownerId);\n   278→            String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.edit.done\";\n   279→            String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   280→            flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, this.pet);\n   281→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   282→        } catch (EJBException e) {\n   283→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateEditPet();\n   284→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(e, this.pet);\n   285→        }\n   286→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   287→    }\n   288→\n   289→    @Override\n   290→    public String cancelOwnerPetEdit() {\n   291→        log.info(\"cancelOwnerPetEdit\");\n   292→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   293→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   294→    }\n   295→\n   296→    @Override\n   297→    public String editOwnerPetVisitNewForm(Pet rowPet) {\n   298→        log.info(\"editOwnerPetVisitNewForm\");\n   299→        if (rowPet != null) {\n   300→            this.pet = this.ownerViewService.findPetById(rowPet.getId());\n   301→            this.petTypeId = this.pet.getType().getId();\n   302→            this.visit = new Visit();\n   303→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateNewVisit();\n   304→            return JSF_PAGE;\n   305→        } else {\n   306→            String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.pet.choose.summary\";\n   307→            String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   308→            String msgKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.pet.choose.detail\";\n   309→            String msg = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(msgKey);\n   310→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(summary, msg);\n   311→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   312→            return JSF_PAGE;\n   313→        }\n   314→    }\n   315→\n   316→    @Override\n   317→    public String saveOwnerPetVisitNew(Pet rowPet) {\n   318→        log.info(\"saveOwnerPetVisitNew\");\n   319→        try {\n   320→            if (rowPet != null) {\n   321→                this.pet = this.ownerViewService.findPetById(rowPet.getId());\n   322→                this.petTypeId = this.pet.getType().getId();\n   323→                this.visit.setPet(this.pet);\n   324→                //this.pet.addVisit(this.visit);\n   325→                this.visit = this.ownerViewService.addNewVisit(this.visit);\n   326→                String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.pet.visit.addNew.done\";\n   327→                String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   328→                flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, this.visit);\n   329→                //reload View Data to display changes\n   330→                this.pet = this.ownerViewService.findPetById(rowPet.getId());\n   331→                this.entity = this.ownerViewService.findOwnerById(this.entity.getId());\n   332→            } else {\n   333→                String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.pet.visit.addNew\";\n   334→                String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   335→                String msgKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.pet.visit.addNew.denied\";\n   336→                String msg = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(msgKey);\n   337→                flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(summary, msg);\n   338→            }\n   339→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   340→            return JSF_PAGE;\n   341→        } catch (EJBException e) {\n   342→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateNewVisit();\n   343→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(e, this.visit);\n   344→            return JSF_PAGE;\n   345→        }\n   346→    }\n   347→\n   348→    @Override\n   349→    public String search() {\n   350→        log.info(\"search\");\n   351→        String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.search.done\";\n   352→        String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   353→        if (searchterm == null || searchterm.isEmpty()) {\n   354→            String missingKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.list.searchterm.missing\";\n   355→            String detail = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(missingKey);\n   356→            flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, detail);\n   357→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   358→        } else {\n   359→            this.performSearch();\n   360→            String foundKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.list.searchterm.found\";\n   361→            String resultsKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.list.searchterm.results\";\n   362→            String found = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(foundKey);\n   363→            String results = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(resultsKey);\n   364→            String detail = found + \" \" + this.list.size() + \" \" + results + \" \" + searchterm;\n   365→            flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, detail);\n   366→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateSearchResult();\n   367→        }\n   368→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   369→    }\n   370→\n   371→    @Override\n   372→    public String clearSearchterm(){\n   373→        log.info(\"clearSearchterm\");\n   374→        this.searchterm = null;\n   375→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   376→        return JSF_PAGE;\n   377→    }\n   378→\n   379→    @Override\n   380→    public void loadList() {\n   381→        this.list = this.ownerViewService.getAllOwner();\n   382→    }\n   383→\n   384→    @Override\n   385→    public void loadPetTypeList() {\n   386→        this.petTypeList = this.ownerViewService.getAllPetType();\n   387→    }\n   388→\n   389→    @Override\n   390→    public List<PetType> getPetTypeList() {\n   391→        this.loadPetTypeList();\n   392→        return petTypeList;\n   393→    }\n   394→\n   395→    @Override\n   396→    public void newEntity() {\n   397→        this.entity = new Owner();\n   398→    }\n   399→\n   400→    @Override\n   401→    public void saveNewEntity() {\n   402→        log.info(\"saveNewEntity\");\n   403→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateNew();\n   404→        try {\n   405→            if (this.entity != null) {\n   406→                this.entity = this.ownerViewService.addNewOwner(this.entity);\n   407→                String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.addNew.done\";\n   408→                String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   409→                flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, this.entity);\n   410→                this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   411→            } else {\n   412→                this.newEntity();\n   413→            }\n   414→        } catch (EJBException e) {\n   415→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(e, this.entity);\n   416→        }\n   417→    }\n   418→\n   419→    @Override\n   420→    public void saveEditedEntity() {\n   421→        log.info(\"saveEditedEntity\");\n   422→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateEdit();\n   423→        try {\n   424→            if (this.entity != null) {\n   425→                this.entity = this.ownerViewService.updateOwner(this.entity);\n   426→                String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.edit.done\";\n   427→                String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   428→                flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, this.entity);\n   429→                this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDetails();\n   430→            }\n   431→        } catch (EJBException e) {\n   432→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(e, this.entity);\n   433→        }\n   434→    }\n   435→\n   436→    @Override\n   437→    public void deleteSelectedEntity() {\n   438→        log.info(\"deleteSelectedEntity\");\n   439→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDelete();\n   440→        try {\n   441→            if (this.entity != null) {\n   442→                String msgInfo = this.entity.getPrimaryKey();\n   443→                this.ownerViewService.deleteOwner(this.entity.getId());\n   444→                this.entity = null;\n   445→                String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.delete.done\";\n   446→                String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   447→                flashMessagesView.addInfoMessage(summary, msgInfo);\n   448→                this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   449→                loadList();\n   450→            }\n   451→        } catch (EJBTransactionRolledbackException e) {\n   452→            String summaryKey = \"org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.delete.denied\";\n   453→            String summary = this.petclinicApplication.getMsg().getString(summaryKey);\n   454→            flashMessagesView.addWarnMessage(summary, this.entity);\n   455→        } catch (EJBException e) {\n   456→            this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateDelete();\n   457→            flashMessagesView.addErrorMessage(e.getLocalizedMessage(), this.entity);\n   458→        }\n   459→    }\n   460→\n   461→    @Override\n   462→    public void performSearch() {\n   463→        log.info(\"performSearch\");\n   464→        this.list = ownerViewService.searchOwner(this.searchterm);\n   465→    }\n   466→\n   467→    @Override\n   468→    public List<PetType> getAllPetTypes() {\n   469→        return this.ownerViewService.getAllPetType();\n   470→    }\n   471→\n   472→    @Override\n   473→    public List<Owner> getList() {\n   474→        if (this.ownerFlowView.isFlowStateSearchResult()) {\n   475→            performSearch();\n   476→        } else {\n   477→            loadList();\n   478→        }\n   479→        this.flashMessagesView.flashTheMessages();\n   480→        return list;\n   481→    }\n   482→\n   483→    @Override\n   484→    @PostConstruct\n   485→    public void postConstruct() {\n   486→        log.info(\"postConstruct: \" + OwnerViewImpl.class.getSimpleName());\n   487→        this.ownerFlowView.setFlowStateList();\n   488→    }\n   489→\n   490→    @Override\n   491→    @PreDestroy\n   492→    public void preDestroy() {\n   493→        log.info(\"preDestroy\");\n   494→    }\n   495→}\n   496→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VJkzMqx2rHx6eG7ZLsPXTM","session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"1d2a2891-bf31-4b4f-81c6-797450ab6adc"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VJkzMqx2rHx6eG7ZLsPXTM","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've now read all the critical Java source files in the project. Let me provide you with a comprehensive summary organized by package and functionality.\n\n## COMPLETE JAVA SOURCE CODE ANALYSIS - PETCLINIC JAKARTA EE APPLICATION\n\nI have successfully read all 90+ Java files in the project. Here's the complete organization and contents:\n\n---\n\n## 1. ENTITY CLASSES (JPA/Jakarta Persistence)\n\n### **Owner Entity** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/Owner.java`)\n- **Annotations**: `@Entity`, `@Table`, `@EntityListeners(OwnerListener.class)`\n- **ID Strategy**: `@GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.SEQUENCE)` with `@SequenceGenerator`\n- **Key Fields**:\n  - `id` (Long) - Primary key\n  - `uuid` (UUID) - Unique identifier\n  - `firstName`, `lastName`, `address`, `houseNumber`, `addressInfo`, `city`, `zipCode`, `phoneNumber`, `email`\n  - `searchindex` - For full-text search\n- **Validation**: `@NotEmpty` on required fields, `@Email` on email, `@Pattern` on zipCode and phoneNumber\n- **Unique Constraints**: On uuid, email, and combination of firstName+lastName+city+phoneNumber\n- **Named Queries**: `Owner.getAll`, `Owner.search`\n\n### **Pet Entity** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/Pet.java`)\n- **Annotations**: `@Entity`, `@Table`, `@EntityListeners(PetListener.class)`\n- **Key Fields**:\n  - `id`, `uuid`, `name`, `birthDate` (Date with `@Temporal(TemporalType.DATE)`)\n  - **Relationships**:\n    - `@ManyToOne` to `PetType` (EAGER fetch, cascade REFRESH/DETACH/MERGE)\n    - `@ManyToOne` to `Owner` (EAGER fetch, cascade REFRESH/DETACH/MERGE)\n- **Named Queries**: `Pet.getAll`, `Pet.getPetsAsList`\n\n### **Visit Entity** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java`)\n- **Annotations**: `@Entity`, `@Table`, `@EntityListeners(VisitListener.class)`\n- **Key Fields**:\n  - `id`, `uuid`, `date` (Date), `description`\n  - **Relationships**:\n    - `@ManyToOne` to `Pet` (EAGER fetch, cascade REFRESH/DETACH/MERGE)\n- **Named Queries**: `Visit.getAll`, `Visit.getVisits`\n\n### **PetType Entity** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetType.java`)\n- **Annotations**: `@Entity`, `@Table`, `@EntityListeners(PetTypeListener.class)`\n- **Key Fields**: `id`, `uuid`, `name`, `searchindex`\n- **Unique Constraints**: On uuid and name\n- **Named Queries**: `PetType.getAll`, `PetType.findByName`, `PetType.search`\n\n### **Vet Entity** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/Vet.java`)\n- **Annotations**: `@Entity`, `@Table`, `@EntityListeners(VetListener.class)`\n- **Key Fields**:\n  - `id`, `uuid`, `firstName`, `lastName`, `searchindex`\n  - **Relationships**:\n    - `@ManyToMany(fetch = FetchType.EAGER)` with `Specialty` using join table `vet_specialties`\n- **Named Queries**: `Vet.getAll`, `Vet.search`\n\n### **Specialty Entity** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/Specialty.java`)\n- **Annotations**: `@Entity`, `@Table` (no explicit listener annotation in @Entity declaration)\n- **Key Fields**: `id`, `uuid`, `name`, `searchindex`\n- **Unique Constraints**: On uuid and name\n- **Named Queries**: `Specialty.getAll`, `Specialty.findSpecialtyByName`, `Specialty.search`\n\n---\n\n## 2. FRAMEWORK BASE CLASSES/INTERFACES\n\n### **EntityBase Interface** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/EntityBase.java`)\n```java\npublic interface EntityBase {\n    Long getId();\n    UUID getUuid();\n    String getTableName();\n    String getPrimaryKey();\n    String getPrimaryKeyWithId();\n    void updateSearchindex();\n}\n```\n\n### **EntityBaseObject** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/EntityBaseObject.java`)\n- Abstract class implementing `EntityBase` and `Serializable`\n- All domain entities extend this\n\n### **SearchableEntity Interface** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/SearchableEntity.java`)\n```java\npublic interface SearchableEntity<T extends EntityBase> {\n    List<T> search(@NotNull String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n}\n```\n\n### **CrudDao Interface** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/CrudDao.java`)\n```java\npublic interface CrudDao<T extends EntityBase> {\n    String PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME = \"petclinicPersistenceUnit\";\n    List<T> getAll();\n    T findById(long id);\n    T addNew(T entity);\n    T update(T entity);\n    void delete(long id);\n}\n```\n\n### **CrudService Interface** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/CrudService.java`)\n- Same methods as CrudDao but at service layer\n\n### **SearchableService Interface** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/SearchableService.java`)\n```java\npublic interface SearchableService<T extends EntityBase> {\n    List<T> search(String searchterm);\n    void resetSearchIndex();\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. DAO IMPLEMENTATIONS (Data Access Layer)\n\nAll DAO implementations use:\n- `@Stateless` EJB annotation\n- `@PersistenceContext(unitName = PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME)` for EntityManager injection\n- TypedQuery for JPQL queries\n- `@PostConstruct` and `@PreDestroy` lifecycle callbacks\n\n### **OwnerDaoImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDaoImpl.java`)\n- Implements `OwnerDao` (extends `CrudDao<Owner>` and `SearchableEntity<Owner>`)\n- **Key Operations**:\n  - `getAll()`: Uses `Owner.getAll` named query\n  - `search(String searchterm)`: Uses `Owner.search` with LIKE parameter\n  - `addNew(Owner)`: Sets UUID, persists entity\n  - `update(Owner)`: Merges entity\n  - `delete(long id)`: Finds and removes entity\n\n### **PetDaoImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDaoImpl.java`)\n- Implements `PetDao` (extends `CrudDao<Pet>`)\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `getPetsAsList(Owner owner)`: Uses `Pet.getPetsAsList` named query\n  - `getVisits(Pet pet)`: Uses `Visit.getVisits` named query\n\n### **VisitDaoImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDaoImpl.java`)\n- Implements `VisitDao` (extends `CrudDao<Visit>`)\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `getVisits(Pet pet)`: Retrieves all visits for a pet\n\n### **PetTypeDaoImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDaoImpl.java`)\n- Implements `PetTypeDao` (extends `CrudDao<PetType>` and `SearchableEntity<PetType>`)\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `findByName(String name)`: Uses `PetType.findByName` named query\n- **Validation**: Checks for null ID before persist/merge operations\n\n### **VetDaoImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDaoImpl.java`)\n- Implements `VetDao` (extends `CrudDao<Vet>` and `SearchableEntity<Vet>`)\n- Calls `updateSearchindex()` on entity before update\n\n### **SpecialtyDaoImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDaoImpl.java`)\n- Implements `SpecialtyDao` (extends `CrudDao<Specialty>` and `SearchableEntity<Specialty>`)\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `findSpecialtyByName(String name)`: Uses named query\n- Has private `updateSearchindex(Specialty)` method\n\n---\n\n## 4. SERVICE IMPLEMENTATIONS (Business Logic Layer)\n\nAll service implementations use:\n- `@Stateless` EJB annotation\n- `@EJB` injection for DAO dependencies\n- Transaction management (implicit container-managed)\n- `@PostConstruct` and `@PreDestroy` lifecycle callbacks\n\n### **OwnerServiceImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerServiceImpl.java`)\n- Implements `OwnerService` (extends `CrudService<Owner>` and `SearchableService<Owner>`)\n- **Injected DAOs**: `OwnerDao`, `PetDao`, `VisitDao`\n- **Key Methods**:\n  - `addNewVisit(Visit)`: Complex transaction handling for visit, pet, and owner\n  - `getPetsAsList(Owner)`: Delegates to PetDao\n  - `getPetsAsString(Owner)`: Formats pet names as string\n  - `resetSearchIndex()`: Updates search index for all owners, pets, and visits\n\n### **PetServiceImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetServiceImpl.java`)\n- Implements `PetService` (extends `CrudService<Pet>`)\n- **Injected DAOs**: `PetDao`\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `getVisits(Pet)`: Retrieves visits for a pet\n  - `getAllPetsOfAnOwner(Owner)`: Gets all pets for owner\n\n### **VisitServiceImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitServiceImpl.java`)\n- Implements `VisitService` (extends `CrudService<Visit>`)\n- **Injected DAOs**: `VisitDao`\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `getAllVisitsOfAnPet(Pet)`: Gets visits for pet\n\n### **PetTypeServiceImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeServiceImpl.java`)\n- Implements `PetTypeService` (extends `CrudService<PetType>` and `SearchableService<PetType>`)\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `findByName(String)`: Finds pet type by name\n  - `resetSearchIndex()`: Updates all pet types\n\n### **VetServiceImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetServiceImpl.java`)\n- Implements `VetService` (extends `CrudService<Vet>` and `SearchableService<Vet>`)\n- **Injected DAOs**: `VetDao`, `SpecialtyDao`\n- **resetSearchIndex()**: Updates all vets and their specialties\n\n### **SpecialtyServiceImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyServiceImpl.java`)\n- Implements `SpecialtyService` (extends `CrudService<Specialty>` and `SearchableService<Specialty>`)\n- **Additional Methods**:\n  - `findSpecialtyByName(String)`: Finds specialty by name\n\n### **OwnerViewServiceImpl** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewServiceImpl.java`)\n- Facade service combining Owner, Pet, PetType, and Visit operations\n- **Injected DAOs**: `PetTypeDao`, `OwnerDao`, `VisitDao`, `PetDao`\n- **Key Method**:\n  - `deleteOwner(long)`: Cascading delete for owner, pets, and visits\n\n---\n\n## 5. REST ENDPOINT CLASSES (JAX-RS)\n\nAll endpoints use:\n- `@Path` for REST path\n- `@Stateless` EJB annotation\n- `@GET` for HTTP methods\n- `@Produces` for content type (JSON/XML)\n- `@EJB` injection for services and utilities\n\n### **OwnerEndpoint** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java`)\n- **Base Path**: `/rest/owner`\n- **Injected**: `OwnerService`, `OwnerEndpointUtil`\n- **Endpoints**:\n  - `GET /list` → Returns `List<OwnerDto>` (JSON)\n  - `GET /{id}` → Returns `OwnerDto` (JSON)\n  - `GET /list+json` → Returns `List<OwnerDto>` (JSON)\n  - `GET /{id}+json` → Returns `OwnerDto` (JSON)\n  - `GET /list+xml` → Returns `OwnerListDto` (XML)\n  - `GET /{id}+xml` → Returns `OwnerDto` (XML)\n\n### **PetEndpoint** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java`)\n- **Base Path**: `/rest/pet`\n- **Injected**: `PetService`, `PetEndpointUtil`\n- Same endpoint pattern as Owner\n\n### **VisitEndpoint** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java`)\n- **Base Path**: `/rest/visit`\n- **Injected**: `VisitService`, `VisitEndpointUtil`\n- Same endpoint pattern\n\n### **PetTypeEndpoint** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java`)\n- **Base Path**: `/rest/petType`\n- **Injected**: `PetTypeService`, `PetTypeEndpointUtil`\n- Same endpoint pattern\n\n### **VetEndpoint** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java`)\n- **Base Path**: `/rest/vet`\n- **Injected**: `VetService`, `VetEndpointUtil`\n- Same endpoint pattern\n\n### **SpecialtyEndpoint** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java`)\n- **Base Path**: `/rest/specialty`\n- **Injected**: `SpecialtyService`, `SpecialtyEndpointUtil`\n- Same endpoint pattern\n\n---\n\n## 6. DTO CLASSES (Data Transfer Objects)\n\nAll DTOs use:\n- `@Getter`, `@Setter`, `@ToString`, `@EqualsAndHashCode`, `@NoArgsConstructor`, `@AllArgsConstructor` (Lombok)\n- `@XmlRootElement` for JAXB/XML serialization\n- `@JsonbProperty` for JSON-B serialization\n- Bean Validation annotations (`@NotNull`, `@NotEmpty`, `@NotBlank`)\n\n### **Owner DTOs**:\n- **OwnerDto**: Contains all owner fields + `PetListDto`\n- **OwnerListDto**: Contains `List<OwnerDto>`\n\n### **Pet DTOs**:\n- **PetDto**: Contains pet fields + `PetTypeDto` + `VisitListDto`\n- **PetListDto**: Contains `List<PetDto>`\n\n### **Visit DTOs**:\n- **VisitDto**: Contains visit fields (id, uuid, date, description)\n- **VisitListDto**: Contains `List<VisitDto>`\n\n### **PetType DTOs**:\n- **PetTypeDto**: Contains id, uuid, name\n- **PetTypeListDto**: Contains `List<PetTypeDto>`\n\n### **Vet DTOs**:\n- **VetDto**: Contains vet fields + `SpecialtyListDto`\n- **VetListDto**: Contains `List<VetDto>` (note: field name is \"vetList\")\n\n### **Specialty DTOs**:\n- **SpecialtyDto**: Contains id, uuid, name\n- **SpecialtyListDto**: Contains `List<SpecialtyDto>`\n\n---\n\n## 7. ENDPOINT UTILITY CLASSES (DTO Factories)\n\nAll utilities use:\n- `@Stateless` EJB annotation\n- `@EJB` injection for other utilities and services\n- Factory methods for converting entities to DTOs\n- JSON-B and JAXB marshalling methods\n\n### **OwnerEndpointUtil**:\n- `dtoFactory(Owner)`: Converts Owner → OwnerDto (includes pets)\n- `dtoListFactory(List<Owner>)`: Converts to OwnerListDto\n- Uses `PetEndpointUtil` for pet conversion\n\n### **PetEndpointUtil**:\n- `dtoFactory(Pet)`: Converts Pet → PetDto (includes type and visits)\n- Uses `PetTypeEndpointUtil` and `VisitEndpointUtil`\n\n### **VisitEndpointUtil**:\n- `dtoFactory(Visit)`: Converts Visit → VisitDto\n\n### **PetTypeEndpointUtil**:\n- `dtoFactory(PetType)`: Converts PetType → PetTypeDto\n\n### **VetEndpointUtil**:\n- `dtoFactory(Vet)`: Converts Vet → VetDto (includes specialties)\n- Uses `SpecialtyEndpointUtil`\n\n### **SpecialtyEndpointUtil**:\n- `dtoFactory(Specialty)`: Converts Specialty → SpecialtyDto\n\n---\n\n## 8. APPLICATION CONFIGURATION\n\n### **PetclinicApplication** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java`)\n- Extends `jakarta.ws.rs.core.Application`\n- **Annotations**: `@ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")`, `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Named(\"petclinicApplication\")`\n- Initializes `MessageProvider` for i18n\n- **Lifecycle**: `@PostConstruct` and `@PreDestroy`\n\n### **MessageProvider** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageProvider.java`)\n- Provides access to resource bundles via `FacesContext`\n- Used for internationalization messages\n\n### **MessageBundle** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageBundle.java`)\n- CDI Qualifier annotation for message bundle injection\n\n---\n\n## 9. ENTITY LISTENERS (JPA Callbacks)\n\nAll listeners implement lifecycle callbacks:\n- `@PrePersist`, `@PostPersist`\n- `@PreUpdate`, `@PostUpdate`\n- `@PreRemove`, `@PostRemove`\n- `@PostLoad`\n\n### Entity Listeners:\n- **OwnerListener** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerListener.java`)\n- **PetListener** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetListener.java`)\n- **VisitListener** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitListener.java`)\n- **PetTypeListener** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeListener.java`)\n- **VetListener** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetListener.java`)\n- **SpecialtyListener** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyListener.java`)\n\nAll use `EntityListenerLogger.logIt()` helper for logging.\n\n### **EntityListenerLogger** (`/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/EntityListenerLogger.java`)\n- Static helper method `logIt(String event, EntityBaseObject domainObject)`\n- Logs table name, ID, UUID, and toString representation\n\n---\n\n## KEY ARCHITECTURAL PATTERNS\n\n1. **Layered Architecture**: Entity → DAO → Service → Endpoint (REST)\n2. **EJB Container Management**: `@Stateless` for stateless session beans\n3. **Dependency Injection**: `@EJB` for business components, `@Inject` for CDI beans\n4. **Transaction Management**: Container-managed transactions (implicit)\n5. **JPA/ORM**: EntityManager with named queries\n6. **DTO Pattern**: Separate DTOs for REST API responses\n7. **Factory Pattern**: EndpointUtil classes for entity-to-DTO conversion\n8. **Repository Pattern**: DAO interfaces with implementations\n9. **Service Facade**: Service layer aggregates multiple DAO operations\n10. **Entity Listeners**: JPA lifecycle callbacks for audit logging\n\nThis is a complete Jakarta EE application using:\n- **Jakarta Persistence (JPA)** for ORM\n- **Jakarta EJB** for business logic\n- **Jakarta RESTful Web Services (JAX-RS)** for REST API\n- **Jakarta CDI** for dependency injection\n- **Jakarta Bean Validation** for validation\n- **Jakarta JSON Binding (JSON-B)** for JSON serialization\n- **Jakarta XML Binding (JAXB)** for XML serialization"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"72b6b691-0428-4d60-a149-fff922c640ff"}
