ind.*` that were no longer needed\n6. **Simplified code** - Removed unnecessary exception declarations and unused helper methods\n\nAll files have been successfully updated and are now compatible with Quarkus CDI!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"991724fb-ee39-4a06-8c1a-a2ad83da6154"}
