{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_019xf49awph7bWzK6f7bvkPL","type":"tool_result","content":"[INFO] Building Petclinic Quarkus 10.0.0.18-SNAPSHOT\n[INFO] --------------------------------[ jar ]---------------------------------\n[INFO] \n[INFO] --- maven-resources-plugin:2.6:resources (default-resources) @ petclinic-quarkus ---\n[INFO] Using 'UTF-8' encoding to copy filtered resources.\n[INFO] Copying 6 resources\n[INFO] \n[INFO] --- quarkus-maven-plugin:3.17.8:generate-code (default) @ petclinic-quarkus ---\n[INFO] \n[INFO] --- maven-compiler-plugin:3.13.0:compile (default-compile) @ petclinic-quarkus ---\n[INFO] Recompiling the module because of changed source code.\n[INFO] Compiling 107 source files with javac [debug release 21] to target/classes\n[INFO] /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/views/LanguageViewImpl.java: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/views/LanguageViewImpl.java uses or overrides a deprecated API.\n[INFO] /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/views/LanguageViewImpl.java: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details.\n[INFO] ------------------------------------------------------------------------\n[INFO] BUILD SUCCESS\n[INFO] ------------------------------------------------------------------------\n[INFO] Total time:  5.467 s\n[INFO] Finished at: 2026-03-14T08:28:55Z\n[INFO] ------------------------------------------------------------------------","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VeFkPFvqPVYBLLwSaYRUtm","session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b14