{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01R5Jk5kzXV7bvitVeBzxNMV","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Let me create a final comprehensive summary document:\n\n## BUILD ANALYSIS SUMMARY: Quarkus Petclinic Application\n\n### MAIN SOURCE CODE COMPILATION STATUS: ✅ SUCCESS\n\nAfter thorough analysis of the Maven build output and Docker build logs, I can confirm that there are **ZERO (0) compilation errors in the MAIN source code** (src/main/java).\n\n### Key Findings:\n\n#### 1. Main Source Code Compilation\n- **Total source files**: 107 Java files in src/main/java\n- **Successfully compiled**: 107 files (100%)\n- **Compilation errors in main source**: **0 (ZERO)**\n- **Build status**: `[INFO] BUILD SUCCESS`\n- **Compiled classes generated**: 107 .class files in target/classes\n\n#### 2. Build Verification Results\n\n**Direct Maven Compilation (mvn clean compile)**:\n```\n[INFO] Compiling 107 source files with javac [debug release 21] to target/classes\n[INFO] BUILD SUCCESS\n[INFO] Total time:  5.929 s\n```\n\n**Error Count Analysis**:\n- Main source errors (src/main/java): **0**\n- Test source errors (src/test/java): **201** (not part of this analysis)\n\n#### 3. What Was Successfully Migrated in Main Source\n\nAll main source files have been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE to Quarkus:\n\n1. **No `javax.*` imports** - All imports properly use `jakarta.*` packages\n2. **No EJB exceptions** - No references to `EJBException` or `EJBTransactionRolledbackException`\n3. **No PrimeFaces dependencies** - `SelectItem` and `DualListModel` have been removed/replaced with plain Lists\n4. **No JSF Converters** - `@FacesConverter` removed, converter classes simplified to plain CDI beans\n5. **Proper CDI annotations** - All beans use `@Named` and `@ApplicationScoped` from Jakarta CDI\n6. **Serializable + ApplicationScoped** - No conflicts (this is acceptable in Quarkus)\n\n#### 4. Key Migration Points Verified\n\n**Entity Classes** (Owner, Pet, Vet, PetType, Specialty, Visit):\n- ✅ Use Jakarta Persistence API (`jakarta.persistence.*`)\n- ✅ Proper entity annotations\n- ✅ No compilation errors\n\n**Service/DAO Classes**:\n- ✅ Use Jakarta CDI (`jakarta.inject.*`, `jakarta.enterprise.context.*`)\n- ✅ Use Jakarta Transaction API (`jakarta.transaction.*`)\n- ✅ Proper dependency injection\n- ✅ No compilation errors\n\n**View Classes** (OwnerViewImpl, VetViewImpl, PetTypeViewImpl, SpecialtyViewImpl, etc.):\n- ✅ Removed PrimeFaces `DualListModel` - replaced with plain `List<T>`\n- ✅ Removed PrimeFaces `SelectItem` - replaced with `Map<String, String>`\n- ✅ Use Jakarta CDI annotations\n- ✅ No compilation errors\n\n**Converter Classes** (PetTypeConverter, SpecialtyConverter):\n- ✅ Removed `@FacesConverter` annotation\n- ✅ Simplified to plain CDI beans with `@ApplicationScoped`\n- ✅ Retained conversion logic methods\n- ✅ No compilation errors\n\n**REST Endpoints**:\n- ✅ Use Jakarta REST (`jakarta.ws.rs.*`)\n- ✅ Proper endpoint annotations\n- ✅ No compilation errors\n\n#### 5. Only Warning (Not an Error)\n\nThe only warning in the main source compilation is:\n```\nLanguageViewImpl.java uses or overrides a deprecated API\n```\n\nThis is merely a deprecation warning (line 63 uses raw `List` type), **NOT a compilation error**.\n\n### CONCLUSION\n\n**There are ZERO (0) compilation errors in the MAIN source code (src/main/java)**. \n\nThe application's main source code has been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE to Quarkus. All 107 source files compile successfully without any errors. The Maven build completes with `BUILD SUCCESS` status.\n\nThe Docker build failure is entirely due to **test code errors** (201 errors in src/test/java), which use testing frameworks like JUnit, Arquillian, and Selenium that are not configured or available in the Quarkus migration. These test errors are outside the scope of the main source code analysis.\n\n### Files with Successful Migration Examples\n\n1. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetViewImpl.java**\n   - Removed DualListModel, using List<Specialty>\n   - All Jakarta imports\n   - Compiles successfully\n\n2. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/views/LanguageViewImpl.java**\n   - Removed SelectItem, using Map<String, String>\n   - All Jakarta imports\n   - Compiles successfully (with deprecation warning only)\n\n3. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/views/PetTypeConverter.java**\n   - Removed @FacesConverter\n   - Simplified to CDI bean\n   - Compiles successfully\n\n4. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewService.java**\n   - Interface exists and is used properly\n   - Compiles successfully"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b5335c7b-0969-4f64-b148-77b8530ff921","uuid":"72414f86-5375-4adc-96b3-35d3014ef5ce"}
